1 (b) Must not be used for capital expenditures, including, without
2 limitation, the construction of new facilities.
3 3. Any balance of the sums appropriated by subsection 1
4 remaining at the end of the respective fiscal years must not be
5 committed for expenditure after June 30 of the respective fiscal
6 years by the entity to which the appropriation is made or any entity
7 to which money from the appropriation is granted or otherwise
8 transferred in any manner, and any portion of the appropriated
9 money remaining must not be spent for any purpose after
10 September 18, 2026, and September 17, 2027, respectively, by
11 either the entity to which the money was appropriated or the entity
12 to which the money was subsequently granted or transferred,
13 and must be reverted to the State General Fund on or before
14 September 18, 2026, and September 17, 2027, respectively.
15 Sec. 1.3. There is hereby appropriated from the State General
16 Fund to the Nevada System of Higher Education the sum of
17 $2,500,000 for the Nevada State University budget account to
18 support academic programming at the North Las Vegas site of the
19 Nevada State University.
20 Sec. 1.5. There is hereby appropriated from the State General
21 Fund to the Nevada System of Higher Education the sum of
22 $1,511,999 for the Western Nevada College budget account for the
23 renovation of the Aspen Building on the campus of Western Nevada
24 College.
25 Sec. 1.7. Any remaining balance of an appropriation made by
26 section 1.3 or 1.5 of this act must not be committed for expenditure
27 after June 30, 2027, by the entity to which the appropriation is made
28 or any entity to which money from the appropriation is granted or
29 otherwise transferred in any manner, and any portion of the
30 appropriated money remaining must not be spent for any purpose
31 after September 17, 2027, by either the entity to which the money
32 was appropriated or the entity to which the money was subsequently
33 granted or transferred, and must be reverted to the State General
34 Fund on or before September 17, 2027.
35 Sec. 2. This act becomes effective on July 1, 2025.
